➜跟爹姓什么时候成了取名的默认选项？
http://www.sohu.com/a/417258702_624188	27776
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200909/99a7362a61114f8ea4358958774310c6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肯定很多人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没点开这篇文章</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就想到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Papi酱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从当时的评论区里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕看到了这样的评论——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200909/88bc4c781fc2411aaae5d1d44a5a69a1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">评论里的<strong>上古八大姓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功的引起了朕的好奇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而仔细一查</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">这还和<strong>姓氏起源</strong>有千丝万缕的关系</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么正好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天就给大家科普一下姓氏起源吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200909/7824a01dc5994f8eb8eca2a6abf9172f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在最开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>姓</strong>和<strong>氏</strong>是两个不同的东西</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先有了姓才有氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那么姓是怎么来的呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200909/5b7c5cd8e0ef4bbcbdbc1b2bd08179b5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让我们把姓字拆开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没错，是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>女 生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以故事就得从<strong>母系社会</strong>说起了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200909/813e549b463845688f9a2f8a286cda86.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在原始社会时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于智力还有限</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">工具不足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">导致打猎这件事就变得——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>非</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>常</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>费</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">负责这项工作的男性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅带不回什么肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可能<strong>连自个儿都带不回来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以四舍五入就跟<strong>消耗品</strong>一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没什么地位和价值</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200909/75c73caa9ab746fe905c07f05f82f2c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相比之下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女性主管了<strong>生育</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在死亡率极高的环境下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">使得<strong>种族能够延续下去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简直就是救世主一样的存在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然地位就会更高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这也就是<strong>母系社会</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200909/8aee74954e9142259f1a881bbfec8503.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问题也来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那时候人们还不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>近亲结婚</strong>会带来的后果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家通常都在部落里面<strong>内部消化</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就这么一代一代地繁殖下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200909/f75b0161414449d484e7d81d2af53045.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出现的后果就是：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一代不如一代</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要再这么下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整个部落未来可能就全是<strong>智障</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是为了部落不团灭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>姓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就产生了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200909/acd4dc5f7f5e4362ae49d3a10f09fdd1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟在母系社会里面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家基本都<strong>没爹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒不是因为爹太渣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是爹真的<strong>太菜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么死了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么留个小蝌蚪就走了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟打猎不太行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还多张嘴吃饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>怪浪费粮食的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200909/73bf1dc0fa654f918e48ad4895686f96.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那么这些姓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>又是由什么而定的呢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200909/5b7c5cd8e0ef4bbcbdbc1b2bd08179b5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一种说法是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>水是万物之源</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而背水真的很累</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以大家建房子组部落的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都爱<strong>靠着水边</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是家住哪条河边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就拿<strong>河的名</strong>当做姓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200909/b2e32366f0c841edb26d95f4b9d018ba.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如你住在<strong>姬水</strong>旁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就姓姬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200909/a341495e13e04eccaa57162d64cfb6c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有一种说法是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这取决于了<strong>第一个妈的特性</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">依旧拿姬来说吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它的<strong>甲骨文</strong>是这样的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200909/62e7f7285f1f47479278518744fbd496.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看上去好像是一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正在对镜子梳妆的女子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而<strong>金文</strong>的姬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200909/fd1f8c31f854408ca856547f7efba5c7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看看左半边像什么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200909/61dbbb572cc6486a8af2ef133576c921.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">证明姬姓的老妈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可能是族群里<strong>丰腴的美人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这样<strong>姬姓的人聚集的多了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那条河才叫做姬水</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200909/6c48522cd90b43c7804b3e3e2a555c43.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下<strong>优生优育</strong>开展开来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">智力和身体都得到了提升</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男性的春天终于来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">工具制造加强</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打猎方面的成功率翻倍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">农耕、畜牧也一块儿发展</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更有力气的男性都占了<strong>优势</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下死亡率大大<strong>降低</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男性地位得到提升</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>父系社会</strong>到来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200909/ddccc9f03cf74f2ba226881f54ade221.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过随之而来的问题就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人死得少生得多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地儿就那么大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不够住了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——于是有部分人就得挪窝了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200909/9786e6c3b1024ec08e84ba587d4bcc40.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搬出去后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家还是一个姓的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>又㕛叒叕</strong>难以辨别了谁是谁了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>氏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就出现了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在最开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">氏的命名主要看<strong>地点</strong>和<strong>职业</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200909/06233c457bd042df85798757b0e081d1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄帝姓<strong>姬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">住在<strong>轩辕丘</strong>那块儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">氏就为<strong>轩辕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而炎帝姓<strong>姜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为是<strong>务农小能手</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">氏就为<strong>神农</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200909/8aee74954e9142259f1a881bbfec8503.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随着部落慢慢变成国家后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>分封制</strong>流行了起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时候的国家老大就开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给关系户们发地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你分到哪块</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>氏就可以叫什么</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以从这时候开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>氏就成了贵族的象征</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平民一般是没有的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200909/91be11ea2eb340deb71723518b74b8b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>既然姓和氏都有了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那么见面该叫什么哪个呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200909/db90acc9096a4c799111251decdbd374.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>春秋战国</strong>时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男的称呼氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女的称呼姓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女姓的叫法组成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200909/0a643728072e4c55820cb7b2c189471b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>夏姬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200909/b642a1c4896d404a83743a78ecde5bb1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>褒姒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200909/a1dd990aebf54d1f896b7dba9cb6e267.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>孟姜女</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200909/27e4bcdc16314950b28805907be6468d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而男性的叫法组成分为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>皇家版</strong>和<strong>普通人版</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>皇家版</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皇亲国戚直接称<strong>爵位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如你需要全文背诵的</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
晋侯、秦伯围郑，以其无礼于晋，且贰于楚也。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——《烛之武退秦师》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>晋侯</strong>就是<strong>晋文公</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秦伯</strong>就是<strong>秦穆公</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而国君的孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>公子+名</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>公子小白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>公子扶苏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>普通人版</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>氏+名</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时候有人就会发现<strong>bug</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>商鞅</strong>明明是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>姬</strong>姓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">名<strong>鞅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">公孙氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为什么却叫了商鞅？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200909/332d9af91b274b419859b8de00854d73.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在那个时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">氏代表的是<strong>家族、封地</strong>等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以<strong>氏是可以变化的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">商鞅在老家的时候可以叫公孙鞅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出去老家闯荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了表明自己卫国国君后代的身份</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就可以叫卫鞅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后来因为工作表现优异</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被赐了<strong>商于十五邑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就变成了商鞅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200909/61bc5e6a345e409b97de49970224acc5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200909/5d42b2b42c904d09a9a5f26aab5a986e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在司马迁的<strong>《史记》</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向来姓氏不分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如他写刘邦就是——</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
高祖，沛丰邑中阳里人，姓刘氏，字季
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——《史记卷八·高祖本纪第八》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于姓和氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到底是哪年哪月开始正式合并的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就没有具体时间点了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过至少从秦灭了六国后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">社会等级一下子<strong>巨变</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贵族变成了平民</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平民飞上了枝头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>氏这种身份等级象征就没啥意义了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>姓慢慢也就取代了氏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到<strong>汉朝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">姓氏差不多完成了合并</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200909/7cf06ec833294377884ed6321eb3116c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
“秦灭六国，子孙皆为民庶，或以国为氏，或以姓为氏，或以氏为氏，姓氏之失自此始。”
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——《通志·氏族略序》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这一切的一切</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后的大赢家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无疑就是<strong>黄帝</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为贼能生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以一个姬姓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">撑起了无数的延伸姓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">占了百家姓<strong>82%</strong>的份额</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200909/53fb432e75c549b6b8c1af1885e7a443.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在新版百家姓里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">排名前三的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>王 李 张</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王和张都是确认来<strong>源于姬姓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">连李姓也有一说来自姬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200909/6ccbaf3d1bf841fd8a52ebf461998863.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再看看隔壁的CP<strong>炎帝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真的是实惨了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200909/69282c29943645f5bce8ca952ff203d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而更重要的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄帝还极有可能是女的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200909/192a9ab396a94f51bb19fa45aa733b4c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">照这么说来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在看起来虽然流行跟爹姓</p>
